## Article content starts here

Below configuration dynamically retrieves a token from Kong's Vault and appends it to the Authorization header as a Bearer token.

## Use headers to organize sections

1. Enable `KONG_UNTRUSTED_LUA="on"` in your {{site.base_gateway}} configuration.

2. Add the following under config.add_headers under Request Transformer Advanced plugin configuration: 

```
    Authorization:$((function() local value, err =
        kong.vault.get("{vault://env/add-your-vault-name-here}") if value then return "Bearer "
        .. value end end)())
```


